                  "title": "Assumption 2.3 (Labor cost function). ‣ 2.2. Firm’s profit maximization problem ‣ 2. Firm-level profit maximization with carbon pricing ‣ Propagation of carbon price shocks through the value chain: the mean-field game of defaults"
