    },
    {
      "type": "Paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "Text",
          "value": {
            "string": "To establish the existence of a CE, an additional assumption is required to ensure market viability. Specifically, there must exist a vector of positive prices and a production schedule that allows for profitable production in all sectors when labor and emission costs are zero."
