                },
                {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "Text",
                      "value": {
                        "string": "4.11"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "target": "S4.Thmtheorem11",
                  "title": "Lemma 4.11. ‣ 4.3. Linear programming MFG Nash equilibrium ‣ 4. Mean-field game approach to a dynamic market model with defaults ‣ Propagation of carbon price shocks through the value chain: the mean-field game of defaults"
                },
                {
                  "type": "Text",
                  "value": {
                    "string": ", we can exchange differentiation and integration over "
