                  "target": "S4.Thmtheorem3",
                  "title": "Proposition 4.3. ‣ 4.1. The optimal default problem of the generic firm ‣ 4. Mean-field game approach to a dynamic market model with defaults ‣ Propagation of carbon price shocks through the value chain: the mean-field game of defaults"
                },
                {
                  "type": "Text",
                  "value": {
                    "string": ", which give"
