                  ],
                  "target": "S4.E40",
                  "title": "In Proof. ‣ 4.3. Linear programming MFG Nash equilibrium ‣ 4. Mean-field game approach to a dynamic market model with defaults ‣ Propagation of carbon price shocks through the value chain: the mean-field game of defaults"
                },
                {
                  "type": "Text",
                  "value": {
                    "string": "), and using both the upper bound "
