                  "target": "S4.Thmtheorem8",
                  "title": "Assumption 4.8 (Properties of Net Demand Functions). ‣ 4.2. Linear programming formulation ‣ 4. Mean-field game approach to a dynamic market model with defaults ‣ Propagation of carbon price shocks through the value chain: the mean-field game of defaults"
